_text = "I open my eyes once again. I am back in the cave, one step closer to the exit. I don't see any memories ahead of me, but I feel this huge wave of emotion consume my thoughts.\n\nI feel my memories flooding back to me.I remember who I am. I remember all the things that make me human. I remember that I love, I get scared and that I make mistakes.\n\nThe flaws, the imperfections, the happy moments, the sad, they all come together to make me. I am made up of these people and the memories I share with those who love me.  These are no longer photographs, but rather reminders to myself of who I am and where I have come from.\n\nI’m not lost in my own thoughts anymore. This is me.\n\nI smile to myself, as I let my first step lead me to the tunnels exit. I leave the tunnel without looking back. "

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, TrainBridgeMemory, TrainBridgeMemory, false)
